@791 = ~Void Weapon~
@792 = ~Void Weapon (Evocation)
Level: 9
Range: 0
Duration: 3 rounds/2 levels
Casting Time: 9
Area of Effect: caster
Saving Throw: none

This spell creates a planar tear in the hands of the mage, that he shapes to give it the shape of a weapon he masters. The blade can not leave his hand for the duration of the spell, unless replaced by another weapon shaped in the same way. This weapon made of void destroys everything that comes in touch with it. It effortlessly penetrates the strongest armors, and gives a +4 bonus to hit. It atomizes the matter around what it hits, inflicting additional 2D6 +4 damage. Finally it can completely disintegrate the victim it affects, if fails a saving throw vs. death at +4.

Note: don't create a two-handed sword or a halberd if you are squipped with a shield; this inconsistency would crash the game. If you want such a weapon, take into consideration to unequip your shield first.~
