@793 = ~Shields of the Exalted~
@794 = ~Shields of the Exalted (Abjuration)
Level: 9
Range: 0
Duration: 2 rounds/level
Casting Time: 9
Area of Effect: caster
Saving Throw: none

This powerful protection spell combines three major protections.
Elemental shield gives a 40% bonus to fire, cold, acid and electricity resistance.
Physical shield gives a 50% bonus against all weapons and a +5 bonus to AC.
Magic shield gives a 15% bonus to magic resistance, +2 to all saving throws (+4 to saving throws vs. spells) and immunity against minor spells (levels 1 and 2).
These 3 protections are inseparable and last until the duration of the spell expires.~
