@797 = ~Mass Control~
@798 = ~Mass Control (Enchantment)
Level: 9
Range: visual range of the caster
Duration: 1 round/level
Casting Time: 9
Area of Effect: 9-meters radius
Saving Throw: negates

By casting this spell, the warlord attempts to take mental control of all creatures in the targeted area. His success depends upon the saving throws of the targets: those who fail a saving throw at -6 are being controlled but keep some semblance of lucidity: any violence against them by the mage or an ally puts control by the spell to an end and frees the creature. Those who are weak enough to fail a saving throw at -2 become puppets under his control, he can do whatever he wants. They can not free themselves from the grip of spell, even if orders given are opposite to their nature.
This spell can only control thinking humanoid creatures. Orders are given by telepathy, there is no barrier of language or culture to prevent controlling.~
