@799 = ~Invulnerability~
@7910 = ~Invulnerability (Abjuration, Necromancy)
Level: 9
Range: 0
Duration: 5 rounds
Casting Time: 4
Area of Effect: caster
Saving Throw: none

Spell of ultimate protection, invulnerability aims to make the warlord truly immortal. During the 5 rounds of the duration of the spell, the wizard is immune to all types of damage, to all effects of death, disintegration, petrification, and generally, to anything that could put an end to his life. In addition, he automatically succeeds all saving throws.
Note: if the wizard is already affected by something harmful when casting the spell, the wound can not kill him for 5 rounds but so far it does not negate, and will continue the harmful effects at the end of the spell. The spell has such a power that it is impossible to keep it for long.~
