@7915 = ~Transformigration~
@7916 = ~Transformigration (Polymorph)
Level: 9
Range: 0
Duration: instantaneous
Casting Time: special
Area of Effect: caster
Saving Throw: none

It's by looking for a way to use magic spontaneously that the warlord discovered this spell, very useful but also expensive.
This strange spell allows to shape the energy stored by the caster when memorizing spells to turn it into whatever spell he knows, at the cost of three times that energy.
In fact, once casting begins, the wizard can choose not matter which spell he knows, and that's this spell that will be casted at the end of casting. The energy expended matches "forgetting" of Transformigration and two other chosen spells from those of higher levels he still has in memory.
Casting Time of this spell depends directly upon the spell that the warlord wants to cast: it matches casting time of the latter.~
